reply_text:
@msbkaioken136 Wtf do you mean it doesn't look like it's gonna be 3 times as bad ? It quite literally does, except Qin vs Hades.
"Manage your expectations better" is pretty funny considering I have 0 expectations for this anime. I usually don't have any for animes so as to not be disappointed, but saying this looks to be better than the last seasons is wild. I never said it would be worse, I said this looks worse as it is right now.
You're so entitled to your opinion trying to make it a universal truth that it's kind of hilarious.

@msbkaioken136 You've made 9 replies repeating your exact same point, which everyone had when season 2 was going to come out, and guess what happened.
Yeah there isn't any variation because the issue is pretty clear here, and it's been clear since season 1. My other comments are mainly jokes, a YouTube comment section isn't the place where I'll write multiple paragraphs with images to analyze why this is just a downgrade overall.
EDIT : Also you seem weirdly pressed about all this, are you good ?
